Modifications
-------------
This work has been substantially modified and extended by the project owner.
Per Section 4(b) of the Apache License, the following are noted as changed or
newly added (non-exhaustive):

  - Reworked into a persistent, multi-issue "saga" creator with a party roster,
    cross-issue continuity and recaps.
  - New modules: types, engine, llm (multi-provider), safety, storage (split
    IndexedDB page store), audio, cameo/cross-over, personas, GM campaign mode.
  - Added Game Master mode (campaign prep + "true story" issue forging,
    optional permadeath), narrator personas, multi-LLM support, optional audio
    narration/music, content-safety layer, and a unit-test suite.

